description:
Perform a comprehensive configuration export of the Nx Witness VMS system using the REST API (https://localhost:7001, admin/Admin1234!). Retrieve the current state of System Info, Servers, Devices (Cameras), Users, Layouts, Event Rules, and System Settings. Compile this data into a single JSON file saved to /home/ga/dr_export/disaster_recovery_config.json using the following structure:

{
  "metadata": {
    "exportTimestamp": "<ISO8601>",
    "systemName": "<name>",
    "exportVersion": "1.0"
  },
  "systemInfo": { ... },
  "servers": [ ... ],
  "devices": [ ... ],
